{"id":8404,"name":null,"username":"Battler","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/battler/{size}/208_2.png","created_at":"2005-04-28T09:16:54.000Z","cooked":"<p><span class=\"bbcode-b\"><span class=\"bbcode-u\">IMPORTANT ANNOUMCENET!!!</span></span></p>\n<p>Me and alexfont are now working on a LBA 2 disassembly project. Were trying to dissasemble the LBA 2 executable file with IDA (Interacitve DisAssembler), which is an excellent disassembler.</p>\n<p><span class=\"bbcode-b\">Now, you would ask, what the heck is the purpose of this?</span><br>\nWell once disassembled the file, we might be able to find out the formats for more LBA files, and also, where some functions in the game are. Think! Maybe we will be able to hack the LBA 2 EXE file to work in RTL! Or to display Arabic letters correctly! And not to mention the life scripts in the scenes! Or many, many other things Just think of the possibilities!</p>\n<p>So, just stay turned and wait for the progress.</p>","post_number":1,"post_type":1,"posts_count":6,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T15:22:47.508Z","reply_count":5,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":3,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":40.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":8401,"topic_slug":"lba-2-disassembly-project","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"raw":"[b][u]IMPORTANT ANNOUMCENET!!!![/u][/b]\n \nMe and alexfont are now working on a LBA 2 disassembly project. We're trying to dissasemble the LBA 2 executable file with IDA (Interacitve DisAssembler), which is an excellent disassembler.\n \n[b]Now, you would ask, what the heck is the purpose of this?[/b]\nWell... once disassembled the file, we might be able to find out the formats for more LBA files, and also, where some functions in the game are. Think! Maybe we will be able to hack the LBA 2 EXE file to work in RTL! Or to display Arabic letters correctly! And not to mention the life scripts in the scenes! Or many, many other things... Just think of the possibilities!\n \nSo, just stay turned and wait for the progress.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":1016,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba-2-disassembly-project/8401/1","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null,"can_vote":false}
{"id":218448,"name":null,"username":"xesf","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/xesf/{size}/122_2.png","created_at":"2005-04-28T09:30:10.000Z","cooked":"<p>This cant be turn into a project.<br>\nIts really difficult to do such thing and will take years.<br>\nWhy you think TwinEngine take so time? Yaz0r had a hard work doing the same for LBA1 and isnt all finished yet.<br>\nDont forget LBA2 is much bigger than LBA1 and have lots and lots of routines to figure out.</p>","post_number":2,"post_type":1,"posts_count":6,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T17:19:26.930Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":8401,"topic_slug":"lba-2-disassembly-project","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":1016,"username":"Battler","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/battler/{size}/208_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"This can't be turn into a project.\nIts really difficult to do such thing and will take years.\nWhy you think TwinEngine take so time? Yaz0r had a hard work doing the same for LBA1 and isn't all finished yet. \nDon't forget LBA2 is much bigger than LBA1 and have lots and lots of routines to figure out.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"group_moderator":true,"user_id":463,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba-2-disassembly-project/8401/2","reactions":